{
  "id": "api/index/class/Scheduler",
  "title": "Scheduler",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"page-actions\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/edit/master/src/internal/Scheduler.ts?message=docs(index)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L5-L90\" aria-label=\"編輯建議\" title=\"編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/tree/7.5.2/src/internal/Scheduler.ts#L5-L90\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n  </div>\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/index\", \"name\": \"rxjs/index\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/index/class/Scheduler\", \"name\": \"Scheduler\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/index\">rxjs/index</a>\n    </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"scheduler\">Scheduler<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/class/Scheduler#scheduler\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label class\">class</label>\n    <label class=\"api-status-label deprecated\">已棄用</label>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  \n\n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-result=\"on\">用於對任務進行排序並安排其執行的執行上下文和數據結構。透過 <code>now()</code> getter 方法提供（可能是虛擬的）時間概念。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">An execution context and a data structure to order tasks and schedule their\nexecution. Provides a notion of (potentially virtual) time, through the\n<code>now()</code> getter method.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">Scheduler 中的每個工作單元都稱為一個 <code>Action</code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Each unit of work in a Scheduler is called an <code>Action</code>.</p>\n\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\nclass <a href=\"api/index/class/Scheduler\" class=\"code-anchor\">Scheduler</a> {\n  now(): number;\n  schedule(work, <a href=\"api/index/function/delay\" class=\"code-anchor\">delay</a>?, state?): <a href=\"api/index/class/Subscription\" class=\"code-anchor\">Subscription</a>;\n}\n</code-example>\n<p></p>\n  \n\n  \n<section class=\"deprecated\">\n  <h2 id=\"deprecation-notes\">棄用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/class/Scheduler#deprecation-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">排程器是 RxJS 的內部實現細節，不應該直接使用。相反，建立你自己的類並實現 <a href=\"api/index/interface/SchedulerLike\"><code>SchedulerLike</code></a>。將在 v8 中內部化。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Scheduler is an internal implementation detail of RxJS, and\nshould not be used directly. Rather, create your own class and implement\n<a href=\"api/index/interface/SchedulerLike\"><code>SchedulerLike</code></a>. Will be made internal in v8.</p>\n\n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n  <section class=\"class-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\nclass <a href=\"api/index/class/Scheduler\" class=\"code-anchor\">Scheduler</a> implements <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/index/interface/SchedulerLike\">SchedulerLike</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/index/class/Scheduler#now\">static now: () => number</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/index/class/Scheduler#constructor()\">constructor(schedulerActionCtor: typeof Action, now: () => number = Scheduler.now)</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/index/class/Scheduler#now\">now: () => number</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/index/class/Scheduler#schedule\">schedule&#x3C;T>(work: (this: SchedulerAction&#x3C;T>, state?: T) => void, delay: number = 0, state?: T): Subscription</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  \n  \n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n  \n  \n\n\n<section class=\"static-properties\">\n  <h2 id=\"靜態屬性\">靜態屬性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/class/Scheduler#靜態屬性\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table properties-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr><th>屬性</th><th>型別</th><th>說明</th></tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n    \n      <tr class=\"static-property\">\n        <td><a id=\"now\"></a><code class=\"\">now</code></td>\n        <td><label class=\"property-type-label\"><code>() => number</code></label></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          \n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    \n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"建構式函式\">建構式函式<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/class/Scheduler#建構式函式\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<a id=\"constructor()\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table constructor\">\n  \n  <tbody>\n    \n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">constructor(schedulerActionCtor: typeof Action, now: () => number = Scheduler.now)</code-example>\n\n\n\n\n  <h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">引數</h4>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table constructor-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"constructor-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>schedulerActionCtor</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n              <p>型別：<code>typeof Action</code>。</p>\n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"constructor-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>now</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n              <p>可選。預設值為 <code>Scheduler.now</code>。</p>\n        <p>型別：<code>() => number</code>。</p>\n        \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <h2 id=\"屬性\">屬性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/class/Scheduler#屬性\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table properties-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr><th>屬性</th><th>型別</th><th>說明</th></tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td><a id=\"now\"></a><code class=\"\">now</code></td>\n        <td><label class=\"property-type-label\"><code>() => number</code></label></td>\n        <td>\n          <p translation-result=\"on\">根據排程器自己的內部時鐘回傳一個表示當前時間（呼叫此函式時）的數字的 getter 方法。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A getter method that returns a number representing the current time\n(at the time this function was called) according to the scheduler's own\ninternal clock.</p>\n\n\n          \n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    \n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"instance-methods\">\n  <h2 id=\"方法\">方法<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/class/Scheduler#方法\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n    <a id=\"schedule\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th><h3 id=\"schedule\">\n    schedule()\n    \n  <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/index/class/Scheduler#schedule\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3></th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p translation-result=\"on\">安排一個函式 <code>work</code> 來執行。根據 <code><a href=\"api/index/function/delay\" class=\"code-anchor\">delay</a></code> 引數（如果指定），可能在將來的某個時間發生。可能會傳遞一些上下文物件 <code>state</code>，它將傳給 <code>work</code> 函式。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Schedules a function, <code>work</code>, for execution. May happen at some point in\nthe future, according to the <code><a href=\"api/index/function/delay\" class=\"code-anchor\">delay</a></code> parameter, if specified. May be passed\nsome context object, <code>state</code>, which will be passed to the <code>work</code> function.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">給定的引數將被處理並存儲為動作佇列中的動作物件。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The given arguments will be processed an stored as an Action object in a\nqueue of actions.</p>\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">schedule&#x3C;T>(work: (this: <a href=\"api/index/interface/SchedulerAction\" class=\"code-anchor\">SchedulerAction</a>&#x3C;T>, state?: T) => void, <a href=\"api/index/function/delay\" class=\"code-anchor\">delay</a>: number = 0, state?: T): <a href=\"api/index/class/Subscription\" class=\"code-anchor\">Subscription</a></code-example>\n\n\n\n\n  <h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">引數</h4>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table instance-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>work</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p translation-result=\"on\">表示任務的函式，或由排程器執行的某個工作單元。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">        A function representing a\ntask, or some unit of work to be executed by the Scheduler.</p>\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>delay</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p>        可選。預設值為 <code>0</code>。</p>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在執行工作之前要等待的時間，其中時間單位是隱式的，由排程器本身定義。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">        Time to wait before executing the work, where the\ntime unit is implicit and defined by the Scheduler itself.</p>\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>state</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p>        可選。預設值為 <code>undefined</code>。</p>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">當排程器呼叫 <code>work</code> 函式時使用的一些上下文資料。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">        Some contextual data that the <code>work</code> function uses when\ncalled by the Scheduler.</p>\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  <h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"回傳值\">回傳值</h4>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">訂閱以便能夠退訂計劃的工作。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code><a href=\"api/index/class/Subscription\" class=\"code-anchor\">Subscription</a></code>: A subscription in order to be able to unsubscribe\nthe scheduled work.</p>\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/deprecations\n - api/index\n - api/index/function/generate\n - api/index/interface/SchedulerLike\n - guide/scheduler\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/index\n - api/index/class/Scheduler#constructor()\n - api/index/class/Scheduler#deprecation-notes\n - api/index/class/Scheduler#now\n - api/index/class/Scheduler#schedule\n - api/index/class/Scheduler#scheduler\n - api/index/class/Scheduler#屬性\n - api/index/class/Scheduler#方法\n - api/index/class/Scheduler#建構式函式\n - api/index/class/Scheduler#靜態屬性\n - api/index/class/Subscription\n - api/index/function/delay\n - api/index/interface/SchedulerAction\n - api/index/interface/SchedulerLike\n - https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/edit/master/src/internal/Scheduler.ts?message=docs(index)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L5-L90\n - https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/tree/7.5.2/src/internal/Scheduler.ts#L5-L90\n-->"
